Package: grattanCharts
Type: Package
Title: Create charts in the style of the Grattan Insitute, Melbourne
Version: 0.4.0.0
Date: 2017-08-27
Authors@R: c(person("Hugh", "Parsonage", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "hugh.parsonage+grattanPackage@grattaninstitute.edu.au"))
Maintainer: Hugh Parsonage <hugh.parsonage@grattaninstitute.edu.au>
Description: The original goal of this package was to simply hold the colours of the Grattan palette. Includes additional useful charting mechanisms.
